<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="J" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Just4" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Just,</orth> adv. exactly, precisely: <cit><quote>now was she j. before him as he sat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 349" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 349</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. in his way,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 349" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 349</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>j. to the time,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 109.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 109, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>have j. our theme of woe,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. as you left them,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.9.6" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. twixt twelve and one,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.6.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 6, 19</bibl></cit>; cf. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 1, 51</bibl> (Evans' speech). <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 22</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.4.51" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.326" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 326</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.286" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 286</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.122" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.117" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.1.171" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 1, 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 4, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.4.28" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 4, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.164" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 164</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 2, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.2.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 2, 2</bibl> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.2.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 2, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 65</bibl> (Qq <emph>jump</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 48</bibl>. <cit><quote>even j.:</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 7</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 3, 13</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>